have a button to add new groups

I like this feature
This is a good feature
I would add an FAQ section here
I like see progress in % and a bar that helps me visualize
With money issues I don't want me photo going out to everyone.

Why is there a search bar for people when the intended use for this application is for friends to transfer funds to friends. Each person should be given a unique identifier to quickly add someone. This isn't facebook. I shouldn't be able to just look anyone up.
Users should not be allowed to operate accounts without an accurate profile picture.
What exactly am I charging someone for?
Are you automatically pulling contacts from social media?
does a charge effectively just send a request to get paid?
Better placeholder profile pictures
FAQ
Clean design that's easy to read.
Home button not really necessary.
What is this used for? Do you search for your friends here, or input a dollar amount?
Is there any way to change this so people can't see what I bought? I'm not super comfortable with everyone knowing what my purchases are.
Are these friends from linked social media accounts, or friends who are also using this site/app?
Why is there "Public" group? This is an app/site designed to transfer money between friends; why would I ever want or need to connect to people I don't know?
Important
Always important
Always want to know when comments I make are public.
Knowing who my friends are is important.
Comments by friends always important.
